params._calldata: A function call, including function selector and arguments                  _calldata is executed with delegatecall on _init
params._diamondCut: Contains the facet addresses and function selectors This argument is tightly packed for gas efficiency     That means no padding with zeros. Here is the structure of _diamondCut: _diamondCut = [     abi.encodePacked(facet, sel1, sel2, sel3, ...),     abi.encodePacked(facet, sel1, sel2, sel4, ...),     ... ] facet is the address of a facet sel1, sel2, sel3 etc. are four-byte function selectors.
params._init: The address of the contract or facet to execute _calldata

facetAddress(bytes4).details: If facet is not found return address(0).

returns._facetFunctionSelectors: The selectors associated with a facet address.
